data.name: ReadElectronicFundTransmission1
data.value: select LAST_UPDATED_BY, SEQUENCE_NUMBER, TRANS_STATUS_CODE, TRANSMISSION_TYPE, TRANSMISSION_ID, TRANS_PROCESS_DATE, FILE_CREATION_DATE, FILE_CREATION_TIME from CKT_ELEC_FUND_TRAN where (TRANSMISSION_TYPE = @transmissionType) and (FILE_CREATION_DATE = @fileCreationDate) and (FILE_CREATION_TIME = @fileCreationTime) and (TRANS_STATUS_CODE = @transStatusCode) and (SEQUENCE_NUMBER >= @sequenceNumber) order by FILE_CREATION_DATE, FILE_CREATION_TIME, SEQUENCE_NUMBER
